x4freetext: 7.6*7.6 cm crystal to be placed perpendicularly
to the beam at a distance of 2 cm from the target.
The alpha detectors were of the silicon surface
barrier type with a specific resistivity of 5000 omega
*cm and 300 omega*cm, and an active area of 40 mm**2.
The targets consisted of thin layers of 6Li enriched
section of the chamber on carbon backings.The thin LiF-
target contained a small gold layer for calibration
